title: Appointments to the Hospital Authority
content_text: The Government announced today (March 23) the appointment of two members and the re-appointment of one member to the Hospital Authority. Professor Lam Shiu-kum and Professor Richard Wong Yue-chim are appointed as members of the Hospital Authority for a period of two years with effect from April 1, 2001. Professor Lam Shiu-kum is Dean of Faculty of Medicine of the University of Hong Kong and an expert in gastroenterology and hepatology. Professor Richard Wong is the Director of the School of Business and The
